Task: Implement extract_gut(zip_path: Path, project_root: Path) -> None

## Implementation
- Function: extract_gut(zip_path: Path, project_root: Path) -> None
- Extracts GUT zip to temp dir using zipfile.ZipFile.extractall
- Locates addons/gut/ via rglob (handles GitHub archive top-level dir like Gut-9.5.0/)
- Copies to project_root/addons/gut/ via shutil.copytree
- Overwrites existing gut dir if present (shutil.rmtree + copytree)
- Cleans up temp dir in finally block (shutil.rmtree with ignore_errors=True)
- Raises GdToolsError with NFR-2 format if addons/gut/ not found in archive

